OpenHPC Tests are available from public git repository.

 - Make sure the slurm is up and running

   $ sinfo

 - Clone the git repository to a NFS shared directory

 - Make sure the directory is visible at compute nodes
   and is NFS mounted wit RW permission at head node,

   $ git clone https://github.com/openhpc/ohpc.git
 
 - cd ohpc/tests/apps/hpcg

 - cp common/TEST_ENV.in common/TEST_ENV

 - Modify TEST_ENV for setting appropriate compiler
   and run time

 - ./run

